{"tid":2157601,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"銅鑼灣sogo門外裝左閉路電視！","createTime":"2020-08-15T06:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T13:25:01.000Z","uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"18969f8e13c115fdd6e46eed64766418c7eb12aa","tid":2157601,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"【銅鑼灣多功能智慧燈柱加裝閉路電視】<br />\n-<br />\n有網民昨晚於Telegram上表示，位於銅鑼灣軒尼詩道崇光百貨門外的多功能智慧燈柱，於昨晚曾進行維修，並增添閉路電視裝置。據本台記者觀察，現場的市民生活一切如常，沒有在意在他們頭上的監控設備。<br />\n-<br />\n攝/編：Stro<br />\n-<br />\n【Multi Functional Smart Lamppost upgraded with CCTVs】<br />\n-<br />\nNetizens reported that repair works has been conducted at the Multi Functional Smart Lamppost at Henessey Road outside SOGO Causeway Bay, with CCTVs allegedly being upgraded.  <br />\n-<br />\nBusiness was as usual for everyone in Causeway Bay as under reporter&rsquo;s observation, nobody seemed to care about the monitoring devices hanging above them.<br />\n-<br />\nPhoto/edited by Stro<br />\n-<br />\n#智能燈柱 #SOGO #軒尼詩道 #銅鑼灣<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\nDR sponsorship programm/DR贊助計畫： <a href=\"https://payme.hsbc/dailyrecord\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpayme.hsbc%2Fdailyrecord&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8UzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=c0498a4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://payme.hsbc/dailyrecord</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHeOA4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHeOA4G.jpg&h=72dee330&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34baa093fc62263bb8e7e29620ba7646fdc29cc1","tid":2157601,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:46:24.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a7c5c5435b59ecb29dda733108947c1bdab23df2","tid":2157601,"uid":79793,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"cit