7601,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a26a6754246b5c34905c94abcca63f348d5c6eb1","tid":2157601,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"之前唔係講咗話唔裝㗎咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s1.stickers.cloud/packs/c82596a4-31b4-4a93-a5f0-3a18146f7aa8/webp/77fc78ed-ffec-43f6-b425-d34f9584a3c5.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.stickers.cloud%2Fpacks%2Fc82596a4-31b4-4a93-a5f0-3a18146f7aa8%2Fwebp%2F77fc78ed-ffec-43f6-b425-d34f9584a3c5.webp&h=258fbb05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e849466396d81963740c117f18f9edba2f4da254","tid":2157601,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"新疆化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80ba66be8c4d119bcca8512f4bc38f75030f82c","tid":2157601,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"智慧燈柱續試推 棄安裝鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n事隔半年多，委員會報告認為，經全面檢視智慧燈柱的設計與運作，以及各項應用功能和技術後，支持政府在智慧燈柱上安裝多項並無私隱問題的裝置。這些裝置包括LED燈、氣象感應器、空氣質素感應器、熱能探測器、無線射頻識別（RFID）標籤、地理二維碼和用作確認燈柱地理位置的藍牙傳送器。<br />\n<br />\n身兼委員會召集人的政府資訊科技總監林偉喬表示，政府會依據委員會的建議，修訂試驗計劃的應用和執行安排，並會爭取相關區議會支持繼續推行計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=84839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2F%3Fp%3D84839&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8UzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=3ad0224a\" target=\"_blank\">http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=84839</a>"},{"pid":"fe0dd2335f17a2221cfba3b12e70165945876054","tid":2157601,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"呢個款應該似係運輸署嗰啲"},{"pid":"f1a7568e40a132d9e897e5adcf3fa2e1335c9968","tid":2157601,"uid":83910,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"而家區區都鬼祟裝緊<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n黑警係咁賣廣告叫商舖安裝CCTV"},{"pid":"77b1086eeb885aa55e3bad809e44b805